---
description: KlickIt dense UI, accessibility and non-generic interaction rules
globs: ["apps/web/**", "packages/ui/**", "packages/printing/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Follow the dense application-shell contracts in blueprint 06.
- Avoid generic card-dashboard templates, excessive whitespace, decorative gradients and oversized hero UI.
- Keep keyboard workflows, visible focus, text labels and accessibility semantics.
- Never rely on color alone.
- English UI first; selected patient messages may be Hindi.
- Show local/cloud mode, active clinic, last sync, pending, failed and conflict states.
